{
  "text": "In fact, we noticed a significant difference in our localization accuracy once we incorporated the information regarding the lines/line intersections as inputs [CITATION_1] . Also, the process is not computationally expensive and we are able to perform the entire visual processing in \u2248 31msec per frame so that the robot is able to operate at frame-rate with \u2248 2msec per frame to spare for other computations.",
